    var index2 = url.indexOf("/", index1 + 1);
    var baseLocalUrl = url.substr(0, index2);
    var apiPartnerServerURL370 = baseLocalUrl + '/services/Soap/u/37.0/'+ sforce.connection.getUserInfo().organizationId;
    var appModel = skuid.model.getModel('Doc_Application');
    var appRow = appModel.data[0];
    var canSettingModel = skuid.model.getModel('CANCongaSettings');
    var canSetting = canSettingModel.data[0];
    var congaQuerylist = skuid.model.getModel('CongaQueries');

    var queryIds = '';
    $.each(congaQuerylist.data, function(i, row){
        if(queryIds !== '') {
            queryIds += ',' + row.Id;
        } else {
            queryIds += row.Id;
        }
    });
    
    var congaTemplateList = skuid.model.getModel('DOC_Conga_Templates');
    var templeteGroups = '';
    $.each(congaTemplateList.data, function(i, row) {
        if(row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c == 'Loan Agreement Common' && appRow.Business_Type__c != 'Sole Proprietorship') {
            if(templeteGroups !== '') {
                templeteGroups += ',' + row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c;
            } else {
                templeteGroups += row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c;
            }
        } else if(row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c == 'Loan Agreement Competitor' && appRow.Total_Competitors_Amount__c > 0 ) {
            if(templeteGroups !== '') {
                templeteGroups += ',' + row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c;
            } else {
                templeteGroups += row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c;
            }
        } else if((appRow.Type__c == 'New' || appRow.Type__c == 'Renewal')
            && (
                (appRow.genesis__Payment_Frequency__c == 'DAILY' && row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c == 'Loan Agreement Daily')
                || (appRow.genesis__Payment_Frequency__c == 'WEEKLY' && row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c == 'Loan Agreement Weekly')
                || (appRow.Type__c == 'Renewal' && row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c == 'Loan Agreement Renewal')
            )
        ) {
            if(templeteGroups !== '') {
                templeteGroups += ',' + row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c;
            } else {
                templeteGroups += row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c;
            }
        } else if (appRow.Type__c == 'Concurrent'
            && (
                (appRow.genesis__Payment_Frequency__c == 'DAILY' && row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c == 'Loan Agreement Concurrent Daily')
                || (appRow.genesis__Payment_Frequency__c == 'WEEKLY' && row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c == 'Loan Agreement Concurrent Weekly')
            )
        ) {
            if(templeteGroups !== '') {
                templeteGroups += ',' + row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c;
            } else {
                templeteGroups += row.APXTConga4__Template_Group__c;
            }
        }
       
    });
    
    const genericParam = canSetting.Conga_Generic_BLA_Parameter__c + '&SC0=1&SC1=SalesforceFile';

    window.open('https://composer.congamerge.com/composer8/index.html?&serverUrl=' + apiPartnerServerURL370 + '&id=' + appRow.Id + genericParam + '&TemplateGroup=' + templeteGroups + '&QueryId=' + queryIds + '&OFN={Template.Label} ' + appRow.Name);

        $.each(newTask.registeredLists,function(){
